name: A night in Lisbon 1/4
description: This one of kind, four panel piece, currently displayed at a Lisbon based FADO event gallery. It is based on  artist's pre-covid travel travel to Lisbon for new years eve of 2020 when covid was spreading around the workd. He created this four part collection of the travel experience in the ensuing lockdown in Chicago during the Summer of 2020. This is a 1st of the four panel series nft collection.
